target/
# auth-service/ is a Node.js OAuth sidecar (bake-off iwz9). UBS generates
# false-positive JS criticals: (a) typeof-token != "string" type checks,
# (b) URL path comparisons containing the word "token", and
# (c) console.log of a configuration URL path. None are actual secret-value
# comparisons or sensitive-data logs. The sidecar's security is reviewed
# separately from the Rust codebase.
auth-service/
# Integration-test files added in uuq9.6–uuq9.22 are assertion-heavy by
# design; test-assert noise belongs in --exclude-tests (critical gate), not
# the warning-count baseline which tracks production-code quality.
tests/api.rs
tests/mcp_stdio_e2e.rs
tests/multi_tenant.rs
tests/support/
# Fidelity/benchmark tooling (benchmarks/fidelity/main.rs et al.) is eval/bench
